00:00:59.840 --> 00:01:01.960
I heard the Princess
fancied the Top Scholar

00:01:02.039 --> 00:01:02.840
at the banquet.

00:01:03.280 --> 00:01:04.920
Soon he'll be summoned
as Prince Consort.

00:01:06.319 --> 00:01:07.519
So he's marrying into royalty?

00:01:08.480 --> 00:01:09.640
So it seems he won't

00:01:09.799 --> 00:01:11.200
pursue an official career, right?

00:01:11.680 --> 00:01:14.239
That is truly a match made in heaven.

00:01:14.239 --> 00:01:17.760
Unless, he has studied himself
into a fool,

00:01:17.760 --> 00:01:20.200
- or he's bound to admire the Princess.
- Exactly.

00:01:32.519 --> 00:01:33.040
My lord.

00:01:40.239 --> 00:01:41.480
Why do you request

00:01:42.000 --> 00:01:43.120
this audience with me?

00:01:50.530 --> 00:01:51.200
Your Highness,

00:01:53.200 --> 00:01:53.799
I...

00:02:03.280 --> 00:02:04.000
I...

00:02:04.159 --> 00:02:06.280
Marrying into royalty
was never my intention.

00:02:07.439 --> 00:02:09.159
You need not worry excessively.

00:02:15.919 --> 00:02:17.719
I know your heart lies with the realm

00:02:19.240 --> 00:02:21.120
and don't want to be trapped
in the palace.

00:02:30.520 --> 00:02:31.240
However, my lord,

00:02:32.000 --> 00:02:33.520
I have another request

00:02:34.400 --> 00:02:35.719
for which I need your assistance.

00:03:40.128 --> 00:03:40.864
For a woman,

00:03:40.864 --> 00:03:42.960
mastering this blade technique
is no small feat.

00:03:43.280 --> 00:03:44.319
If you can't keep up,

00:03:44.520 --> 00:03:45.439
don't force it.

00:03:46.439 --> 00:03:47.439
What of being a woman?

00:03:48.039 --> 00:03:49.439
Whether in letters or arms,

00:03:49.919 --> 00:03:51.199
I aim to be the best.

00:04:11.319 --> 00:04:12.159
Thank you, Master.

00:04:17.664 --> 00:04:19.232
You asked me to persuade His Majesty

00:04:19.552 --> 00:04:22.040
that you shouldn't be bound
by the training of a noble lady.

00:04:23.639 --> 00:04:24.480
Why endure

00:04:25.199 --> 00:04:25.920
such hardship?

00:04:31.439 --> 00:04:32.319
To learn for insight,

00:04:32.480 --> 00:04:33.480
to know the world,

00:04:33.879 --> 00:04:35.240
not to be tied down by romance.

00:04:36.064 --> 00:04:40.064
We train to protect ourselves

00:04:40.510 --> 00:04:41.410
and our loved ones.

00:04:41.920 --> 00:04:43.399
Is that not also true for you?

00:04:50.959 --> 00:04:53.120
It was you who proposed
rejecting the marriage.

00:04:56.000 --> 00:04:58.720
It was also you who suggested
confining the Grand Princess

00:04:58.959 --> 00:05:00.040
in Weiyang Palace.

00:05:01.160 --> 00:05:03.519
And now, it is still you who reveal
your true feelings.

00:05:04.319 --> 00:05:06.360
Your heart is truly fickle.

00:05:07.279 --> 00:05:08.720
Without facing life and death,

00:05:13.920 --> 00:05:15.920
how could one see their true heart?

00:05:16.839 --> 00:05:18.160
After the fire at Weiyang Palace,

00:05:19.160 --> 00:05:21.160
I regretted every day.

00:05:24.480 --> 00:05:26.639
I regretted why I wasn't
in the capital at that time.

00:05:27.279 --> 00:05:29.480
I regretted why I wasn't
in Weiyang Palace at that time.

00:05:29.600 --> 00:05:32.560
I regretted why it wasn't me
who perished in the flames.

00:05:38.439 --> 00:05:39.480
If it had been me,

00:05:42.639 --> 00:05:44.600
I would have ended this torment sooner.

00:05:48.120 --> 00:05:49.120
Lest I grow gray

00:05:50.480 --> 00:05:51.720
too soon and be ashamed

00:05:53.879 --> 00:05:55.240
to face the beloved.

00:06:00.680 --> 00:06:02.519
The person standing before you now

00:06:04.240 --> 00:06:06.240
harbors not a shred
of romantic sentiment.

00:06:09.000 --> 00:06:11.240
Only the flames of vengeance
burn within.

00:06:12.720 --> 00:06:13.720
My feelings toward you

00:06:15.199 --> 00:06:17.560
contain not the slightest trace
of affection.

00:06:22.720 --> 00:06:24.360
I merely wish to use your influence

00:06:24.736 --> 00:06:26.279
to make things more convenient.

00:06:32.670 --> 00:06:33.440
What are you doing?

00:06:48.519 --> 00:06:49.600
Don't worry, Your Highness.

00:06:51.800 --> 00:06:53.079
For the pain you endured,

00:06:54.279 --> 00:06:55.399
I will make them pay

00:06:57.519 --> 00:07:01.319
a hundredfold, a thousandfold.

00:07:09.440 --> 00:07:10.496
(Chaohuang Academy)

00:07:21.480 --> 00:07:23.199
I heard the relief funds came by magic,

00:07:23.399 --> 00:07:25.480
cast by the late Grand Princess's spirit

00:07:25.639 --> 00:07:26.720
for the people.

00:07:29.240 --> 00:07:31.000
It was the ill-gotten wealth of Su.

00:07:32.680 --> 00:07:33.360
Watch your words.

00:07:34.040 --> 00:07:34.959
If that were true,

00:07:35.240 --> 00:07:37.480
then the Grand Princess
could not abide corruption.

00:07:37.879 --> 00:07:38.959
The Grand Princess's spirit

00:07:39.160 --> 00:07:40.519
still cares for the realm.

00:07:46.528 --> 00:07:47.810
(Elegy)

00:07:55.800 --> 00:07:57.160
The fourth year of the Jialin era,

00:07:57.399 --> 00:08:00.079
the first day
of the tenth month, at noon.

00:08:00.639 --> 00:08:04.720
I, Xie Fei, together with the Governor
of Zhuozhou and its people,

00:08:05.600 --> 00:08:08.000
offer sacrifice to the Grand Princess
of the Sheng clan.

00:08:08.519 --> 00:08:10.279
In these turbulent times,

00:08:11.240 --> 00:08:12.879
you set order amidst chaos,

00:08:13.399 --> 00:08:14.519
supported the new Emperor,

00:08:15.140 --> 00:08:16.560
bestowed grace upon the new reign,

00:08:17.399 --> 00:08:18.600
worked night and day,

00:08:18.920 --> 00:08:20.279
remained vigilant until dawn,

00:08:20.680 --> 00:08:22.000
devoted to the nation and duties,

00:08:22.439 --> 00:08:23.839
upheld the law to this day,

00:08:24.260 --> 00:08:25.600
and loved the people as your own,

00:08:26.279 --> 00:08:27.759
treating their suffering as yours.

00:08:28.759 --> 00:08:30.319
The realm turned its gaze to you,

00:08:31.680 --> 00:08:34.279
and the court held you
in solemn reverence.

00:08:35.600 --> 00:08:36.840
We humbly offer this sacrifice.

00:08:43.279 --> 00:08:44.720
Well, Your Highness,

00:08:45.639 --> 00:08:47.679
I perform rites for you,

00:08:48.279 --> 00:08:49.080
burning offerings.

00:08:50.279 --> 00:08:51.080
In your magnanimity,

00:08:51.279 --> 00:08:52.399
may you now rest in peace.

00:08:53.240 --> 00:08:54.399
Don't come for me anymore.

00:08:54.600 --> 00:08:55.600
Don't come for me.

00:08:56.519 --> 00:08:57.519
Don't come for me.

00:08:58.679 --> 00:08:59.559
Everyone,

00:09:01.240 --> 00:09:03.919
the four hundred thousand silver taels
from Chaohuang Academy

00:09:04.159 --> 00:09:06.559
were summoned
by the late Grand Princess's spirit,

00:09:06.720 --> 00:09:08.360
using otherworldly forces

00:09:08.559 --> 00:09:10.440
to aid the displaced.

00:09:10.799 --> 00:09:12.440
The Grand Princess's love for the people

00:09:14.159 --> 00:09:16.039
is witnessed by heaven and earth.

00:09:16.159 --> 00:09:17.080
Your Highness,

00:09:17.159 --> 00:09:19.120
you are the very source
of our livelihood!

00:09:19.392 --> 00:09:20.519
Without the Grand Princess,

00:09:20.960 --> 00:09:22.200
there'd be no land for grain.

00:09:22.600 --> 00:09:23.360
Without grain,

00:09:23.720 --> 00:09:25.480
the people would suffer.

00:09:25.600 --> 00:09:27.440
The Grand Princess
promoted women's education.

00:09:27.440 --> 00:09:28.759
Who says women are inferior?

00:09:28.960 --> 00:09:30.399
Because women's education thrived,

00:09:30.639 --> 00:09:32.799
we avoided the decline into moral decay.

00:09:32.840 --> 00:09:33.840
May the spirits bless me.

00:09:34.039 --> 00:09:34.919
Please, bless me!

00:09:42.960 --> 00:09:43.879
What...

00:09:44.720 --> 00:09:45.960
W-What's happening?

00:09:46.039 --> 00:09:47.879
Oh, my! An omen from the sky!

00:09:48.120 --> 00:09:50.320
Is it the Grand Princess's
wronged spirit crying out?

00:09:50.480 --> 00:09:52.000
Someone! Everyone, look!

00:09:52.120 --> 00:09:53.480
The Grand Princess is enraged!

00:09:54.519 --> 00:09:55.759
Why would it burn us?

00:09:55.879 --> 00:09:57.399
The Grand Princess punishes the evil.

00:09:57.559 --> 00:09:59.399
She cherishes us common folk the most.

00:10:00.480 --> 00:10:01.639
May the spirits bless me.

00:10:17.639 --> 00:10:18.799
Ghosts!

00:10:19.000 --> 00:10:20.120
Ghosts!

00:10:26.159 --> 00:10:27.440
The Grand Princess's manifested!

00:10:27.720 --> 00:10:28.519
She's manifested!

00:10:29.039 --> 00:10:30.240
She's manifested!

00:10:34.759 --> 00:10:36.159
Your Highness, calm your wrath!

00:10:36.639 --> 00:10:39.879
I will use all four hundred thousand
silver taels

00:10:40.039 --> 00:10:41.639
solely for the disaster victims

00:10:42.000 --> 00:10:44.080
in the Grand Princess's name.

00:10:45.840 --> 00:10:47.440
(Flames that can't kill me)

00:10:48.159 --> 00:10:49.919
(shall become my sharpest weapons.)

00:10:50.720 --> 00:10:51.960
(Grudges from my past life)

00:10:52.840 --> 00:10:54.519
(will be paid back with blood.)

00:10:55.799 --> 00:10:57.159
(The innocence of the Sheng clan)

00:10:57.159 --> 00:10:58.480
(shall see the light of day.)

00:10:59.639 --> 00:11:01.519
(I, the fierce ghost,)

00:11:02.559 --> 00:11:04.120
(will grant you no peace.)

00:11:22.919 --> 00:11:26.039
This is Su Wei's lightning rod
disguised as a ritual vessel.

00:11:26.399 --> 00:11:27.879
I'll have someone destroy it shortly.

00:11:27.960 --> 00:11:28.960
I'll handle it myself.

00:11:29.279 --> 00:11:31.120
Actually, you could leave
these matters to me.

00:11:32.000 --> 00:11:33.679
I don't wish you to dirty your hands

00:11:36.799 --> 00:11:37.960
over these things.

00:11:48.200 --> 00:11:49.799
(I chose vengeance myself.)

00:11:50.600 --> 00:11:52.080
(I have to kill them myself,)

00:11:53.480 --> 00:11:54.399
(not anyone else.)

00:11:56.879 --> 00:11:57.759
I am not afraid!

00:12:11.240 --> 00:12:12.240
These hands of mine

00:12:13.279 --> 00:12:14.840
once shielded the Chen State.

00:12:15.879 --> 00:12:18.399
Now, they crawl only through mud.

00:12:19.519 --> 00:12:21.200
I will drag those who deserve death

00:12:22.320 --> 00:12:23.480
back to the underworld

00:12:24.559 --> 00:12:26.200
one by one.

00:12:49.840 --> 00:12:51.559
I will walk this path with you.

00:12:51.919 --> 00:12:54.480
If you wish to send those fiends
to the underworld,

00:12:56.039 --> 00:12:57.440
I will carve

00:12:58.480 --> 00:13:00.559
a bloody path
straight to the underworld for you.

00:13:00.960 --> 00:13:02.840
If you wish to end them yourself,

00:13:04.879 --> 00:13:05.960
I will sharpen

00:13:07.120 --> 00:13:08.240
your blade.

00:13:08.960 --> 00:13:09.960
Once this blade is drawn,

00:13:12.559 --> 00:13:13.639
blood must flow.

00:13:21.120 --> 00:13:21.759
Your Highness,

00:13:22.440 --> 00:13:24.919
I never dreamed
I'd see you again in this life.

00:13:25.840 --> 00:13:26.960
When the news came,

00:13:27.240 --> 00:13:28.200
we all thought...

00:13:30.039 --> 00:13:31.440
If not for Grand Tutor Xie,

00:13:31.679 --> 00:13:33.720
we would have followed you in death,

00:13:34.279 --> 00:13:36.759
so you wouldn't be alone
on the road to the underworld.

00:13:37.720 --> 00:13:39.320
The Grand Princess committed treason.

00:13:40.519 --> 00:13:41.480
She deserves deaths.

00:13:46.440 --> 00:13:48.159
Why do you cling to her memory so?

00:13:48.840 --> 00:13:49.600
We all know

00:13:49.600 --> 00:13:51.559
you would never commit treason.

00:13:52.200 --> 00:13:53.600
Your reign saw

00:13:53.600 --> 00:13:55.159
thriving farms, a strong economy,

00:13:55.360 --> 00:13:57.160
and schools for women,
earning wide praise.

00:13:57.480 --> 00:13:59.159
You were a pillar of Chen State.

00:14:00.320 --> 00:14:01.639
If not for you back then,

00:14:02.320 --> 00:14:03.840
we'd have perished years ago.

00:14:05.200 --> 00:14:06.720
Guarding your academy

00:14:07.120 --> 00:14:08.360
is our future.

00:14:21.039 --> 00:14:21.720
Hua,

00:14:22.919 --> 00:14:24.279
the path I tread now

00:14:25.159 --> 00:14:25.960
is never easy.

00:14:26.279 --> 00:14:27.879
We are willing to follow you.

00:14:28.200 --> 00:14:30.320
Through fire and fury,
I'll never regret.

00:14:30.320 --> 00:14:31.679
(Su Wei betrayed his master.)

00:14:31.679 --> 00:14:33.360
A blood feud can be avenged in time.

00:14:34.200 --> 00:14:36.000
Wronged souls rest in peace
at Weiyang Palace.

00:14:39.360 --> 00:14:40.759
The silver case is just a start.

00:14:41.720 --> 00:14:43.159
Su Wei was struck dead by lightning.

00:14:44.190 --> 00:14:45.980
People sought justice
for the Grand Princess.

00:14:47.480 --> 00:14:50.039
These reports will soon
reach the palace.

00:14:50.320 --> 00:14:52.600
The Ministries of Revenue and Rites
will petition tomorrow

00:14:53.960 --> 00:14:57.080
